Creation of a table :

CREATE TABLE products(

	id INT,
    name STRING,
    price MONEY,
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
  

)

------------------> This creates a new table with columns id, name and price


Inserting into a table:

INSERT INTO products
VALUES (1, 'United States Of America', 2000000000)
  

INSERT INTO products
VALUES (2,'Soviet Union', 1500000000)








